    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/180dfe0cb7919d1f40703742c126217c.poster.avif?t=1759289337\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/180dfe0cb7919d1f40703742c126217c.webm?t=1759289337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/180dfe0cb7919d1f40703742c126217c.mp4?t=1759289337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>登场的女主角皆有全程配音！<br></li><li>游玩时间：20小时～</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事大纲</h2>青蓝岛──施行特殊条例的乐园岛屿。<br>不过岛上依然存在着不愿遵守条例的人们。<br><br>喜欢同性，除了哥哥以外无法接受异性的妹妹。<br>时常被误会的辣妹同学。<br>因为身材娇小，而被误认为未达条例年龄的前辈。<br>以及对自己抱有强烈自卑感的少年。<br><br>主角──橘淳之介与这样的少女们在暗中集结，<br>组成了反对条例的秘密组织【NLNS】。<br><br>提供他们秘密基地，并出钱赞助的【神秘老人】所提出的条件只有一个，<br>就是「找出某位少女，并保护她」。<br>──据说该名少女便是能够摧毁岛上的条例的关键。<br><br>既然如此，要做的只有一件事──<br>欺骗敌对组织，保护自己，并找出那名少女。<br>然後──摧毁可恶的条例！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/0782b48417687246e43c95a23bf6f734.poster.avif?t=1759289337\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/0782b48417687246e43c95a23bf6f734.webm?t=1759289337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/0782b48417687246e43c95a23bf6f734.mp4?t=1759289337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >登场角色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/70c37d6754dad25f9ac28c6d6a948e5f.avif?t=1759289337\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br>片桐奈奈濑<br>（CV：柳ひとみ/Hitomi Yanagi）<br>校内最有名的？？领袖。<br>不时会传出创下壮举的传闻。<br>她反过来利用这些传闻，与主角一起迴避着条例的限制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399220/extras/5857bea66b765224eb705475db6f06d4.avif?t=1759289337\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br>橘 麻沙音<br>（CV：そらまめ。/Soramame）<br>主角的妹妹，也是最瞭解他的人。<br>虽然对男性没兴趣，但非常喜欢哥哥和女孩子，<br>对比自己年长的人和辣妹特别没抵抗力。<br><br>渡会雏见<br>（CV：飴川紫乃/Shino Amekawa）<br>因为非常娇小，怎麽看都太年少而被认为不适用「条例」，<br>但其实是三年级生的前辈。<br>心胸无比开阔，可以靠满溢的母性包容一切。<br>连主角都会忍不住被雏见的包容力所折服。",
